France’s Gimaex, Turkey’s Katmerciler to Set Up Joint Company

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 
2011-09-08T09:47:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/france-s-gimaex-turkey-s-katmerciler-to-set-up-joint-company.html
France ’s Gimaex International and
 Turkey ’s Katmerciler Arac Ustu Ekipman Sanayi & Ticaret AS
agreed to set up a joint company to produce equipment for fire
engines, Katmerciler said in an e-mailed statement today.  Katmerciler General Manager Mehmet Katmerci and Gimaex
Group Chairman Philippe Mis signed the agreement at
Katmerciler’s factory in the industrial zone in Izmir, Turkey,
according to the statement.  Each company will own 50 percent of the venture, which will
focus on exporting from Turkey, Katmerciler said. Production is
due to start in October at an almost completed, $6 million
factory in Izmir, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  